  <brief_title>Bioequivalence of Two Ciprofloxacin 0.3%/Dexamethasone 0.1% Sterile Otic Suspensions in Otitis Media in Children With Tympanostomy Tubes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel Design, Multiple-Site Study to Evaluate the Clinical Equivalence of Ciprofloxacin 0.3%/Dexamethasone 0.1% Sterile Otic Suspension (Par) Compared to CIPRODEX速 (Ciprofloxacin 0.3%/Dexamethasone 0.1%) Sterile Otic Suspension (Alcon) in the Treatment of Acute Bacterial Otitis Media in Children With Patent Tympanostomy Tubes</official_title>
