  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to compare the relative efficacy and safety of the test
      formulation of ciprofloxacin 0.3%/dexamethasone 0.1% sterile otic suspension (Par) to the
      already-marketed formulation CIPRODEX速 (ciprofloxacin 0.3%/dexamethasone 0.1%) sterile otic
      suspension (Alcon) in the treatment of acute bacterial otitis media in children with patent
      tympanostomy tubes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
